165
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:57,176
(Diundang ke perjamuan untuk berterima kasih atas
bantuan Tuan Muda Su dan Nona Shuangshuang)

166
00:13:04,603 --> 00:13:05,564
Paduan emas perak.

167
00:13:06,324 --> 00:13:07,123
Tuan Muda.

168
00:13:07,804 --> 00:13:09,643
